snippet.title: New Interface Demo
snippet.description:
This is a demonstration of the new ManagerLeague interface whcih will go live in just over a day!
And yes, sacking players is still possible, haha!
Anyway, bear with me, and I apologize for the somewhat sore throat from seasonal allergies.
- Spinner
https://www.managerleague.com
